## Key API Endpoints Roadmap (Django REST Framework)

### Authentication & Profiles
* `POST /api/auth/login/` (JWT generation)
* `GET/PUT /api/profiles/dependents/` (Family Guardian managing kids/parents)
* `GET/PUT /api/profiles/me/health-data/` (Managing chronic diseases, heights, weights)

### OCR & Records Processing
* `POST /api/records/upload/` (Triggers `MedicalDocument` creation & Celery Task for OCR)
* `GET /api/records/{id}/metrics/` (Retrieves structured `ExtractedMetric` data)
* `GET /api/records/history/` (Graphing Blood Sugar / Hemoglobin over time)

### Triage Bot
* `POST /api/triage/start/` (Initiate a new `TriageSession`)
* `POST /api/triage/{session_id}/message/` (Send user text, trigger LLM response)
* `GET /api/triage/doctor-queue/` (For Doctors: viewing `ClinicalSummary` objects flagged as 'high' severity)

### Appointments & Reminders
* `GET /api/calendar/doctor/{doctor_id}/slots/` (View availability)
* `POST /api/calendar/book/` (Create `HealthEvent` for 'appointment')
* `POST /api/calendar/medicine-tracker/` (Create `HealthEvent` for 'medicine' with RRULE recurrence)
